structure.unit: DIVISION OF INSURANCE AND INSURANCE GENERALLY (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 21, sec. 2. -- Repealed and reenacted 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 106, sec. 2, effective June 17, 1948. -- Created 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 100, sec. 2, effective October 1, 1947.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Kinds of insurance and insurance companies to which KRS 296.530 to 296.680 apply; coverage by other laws; designation as to which law to apply.
